data.title: ZIP Code Mira (Chontahuasi) in Mira - Ecuador
data.meta_description: The parish Mira (Chontahuasi), Mira, Carchi has 1 ZIP(s) code(s) assigned to its area. Check the map to find out which ZIP code  (040302) applies to the address you are looking for.
data.text:
The parish Mira (Chontahuasi), canton of Mira, in Carchi province has assigned only one ZIP Code for all address in this parish. You can check the area of the ZIP Code 040302, which is the ZIP Code assigned to this parish and check if the address that you are looking for belongs to this postal zone.
